sections.text:
To understand the potential impact and effectiveness of interventions, proper classification is essential. Interventions intended to aid patients in their control of hypertension were compared to standard care.

The interventions include:

(1) mHealth;

(2) Telehealth;

(3) mHealth & telehealth First, whether the intervention was a form of telehealth was determined. Secondly, the intervention was assessed if it was mobile-based. Studies were therefore classified into either (1) mHealth; (2) telehealth; or (3) mHealth & telehealth.
